<h2>Available courts in Barcelona metropolitan area</h2>
<p>Here [Padels.org] will publish the list of available courts and clubs for playing padel in Barcelona metropolitan area.</p>
<p>Please send us the court or club contact data (full address, phone, email, website,...) where you play padel and the padel details (number of courts, rent prizes for members and non-members, indoor/outdoor,...) and if you can a picture.

<div class='well'>
  
     <%= link_to 'Publish your court', new_court_path, class:'btn btn-success pull-right' %>

    <%# if @matchs.exists? %>  
    <table class='table table-striped'>
      <tr>
        <th>Picture</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Full Address</th>
        <th>Phone</th>
        <th>Email</th>
        <th>Website</th>
        <th>Number of courts</th>
        <th>Prizes</th>
        <th>Comments</th>
      </tr>
<%# @matchs.each do |match| %>
      <tr>
      <td><%#= match.date %></td>
      <td><%#= match.court %></td>
      <td><%#= match.player1 %> + <%#= match.player2 %></td>
      <td><%#= match.player3 %> + <%#= match.player4 %></td>
      <td><%#= match.set1 %> , <%#= match.set2 %> , <%#= match.set3 %></td>
      <td><%#= match.description %></td>
      </tr>
      <%# end %>

    </table>
      <%#= will_paginate @matchs %>
    <%# else %>
    <P> There are not courts still published</P>
   <%# end %>

</div>
